Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fvitamin-deficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeficiency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20taking%20a%20supplement%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20a%20healthcare%20professional%20could%20be%20wise%2C%20Bloomer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20most%20Americans%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fvitamin-d-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeficient%20in%20vitamin%20D%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20we%20mainly%20get%20it%20from%20sunlight%2C%20he%20said.%20Vitamin%20D%20is%20essential%20for%20bone%2C%20teeth%2C%20and%20muscle%20health%2C%20so%20he%20takes%20a%20supplement%20every%20day%20to%20ensure%20he%20gets%20enough.%20Bloomer%20previously%20shared%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplement-scientist-heart-health-inflammation-daily-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour%20supplements%20he%20takes%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20vegans%2C%20who%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20deficient%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fvitamin-b12-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evitamin%20B12%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20found%20in%20animal%20products%2C%20are%20advised%20to%20take%20a%20supplement.%20Vitamin%20B12%20keeps%20the%20nervous%20system%20healthy%2C%20supports%20the%20production%20of%20DNA%20and%20red%20blood%20cells%2C%20and%20maintains%20healthy%20brain%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fvitamin-deficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVitamin%20deficiencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20cause%20a%20number%20of%20symptoms%2C%20such%20as%20bleeding%20gums%2C%20mouth%20ulcers%2C%20and%20brittle%20nails%2C%20but%20it's%20best%20to%20get%20checked%20out%20by%20a%20medical%20professional%20