%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IMD%20on%20Monday%20warned%20that%20India%20will%20suffer%20extreme%20heat%20from%20April%20to%20June%2C%20with%20the%20central%20and%20western%20peninsular%20regions%20anticipated%20to%20be%20worst%20affected.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20going%20to%20be%20very%20challenging%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20Since%20we%20are%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20world%20and%20face%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20absolutely%20necessary%20for%20India%20to%20prepare%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-set-to-face-extreme-weather-conditions-between-april-june%2Farticleshow%2F108946718.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFirst%20Burn%20Wives'%20Sarees%26quot%3B%3A%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20Slams%20Rivals'%20India%20Boycott%20Call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20demanding%20a%20boycott%20of%20Indian%20products%20must%20declare%20how%20many%20Indian%20sarees%20their%20wives%20have%20and%20why%20they%20are%20not%20setting%20these%20on%20fire%2C%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20ruling%20Awami%20League%2C%20of%20which%20she%20is%20the%20president%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20tore%20into%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20leaders%20calling%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20Indian%20products.%20%26quot%3BMy%20question%20is%2C%20how%20many%20Indian%20sarees%20do%20their%20wives%20have%3F%20And%20why%20are%20they%20not%20taking%20the%20sarees%20from%20their%20wives%20and%20setting%20them%20on%20fire%3F%20Please%20ask%20BNP%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20secured%20the%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20office%20in%20the%20elections%20held%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20said%20that%20when%20the%20BNP%20was%20in%20power%2C%20ministers%20and%20their%20wives%20would%20buy%20sarees%20on%20India%20trips%20and%20sell%20them%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20then%20moved%20to%20Indian%20spices%20and%20their%20role%20in%20Bangladesh's%20kitchens.%20%26quot%3BGaram%20masala%2C%20onions%2C%20garlic%2C%20ginger%2C%20all%20spices%20that%20come%20(from%20India)%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20their%20(BNP%20leaders')%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20came%20after%20BNP%20leader%20Ruhul%20Kabir%20Rizvi%20threw%20away%20his%20Kashmiri%20shawl%20on%20the%20road%20as%20a%20symbolic%20protest%20against%20Indian%20products%2C%20The%20Daily%20Star%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20are%20taking%20place%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20an%20'India-Out'%20campaign%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Launched%20by%20some%20activists%20and%20influencers%20and%20backed%20by%20a%20section%20of%20Opposition%20politicians%2C%20the%20campaign%20has%20gathered%20steam%20after%20the%20Awami%20League's%20recent%20victory%20in%20an%20election%20boycotted%20by%20the%20Opposition%20BNP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20involved%20in%20the%20campaign%20claim%20India%20has%20been%20backing%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20power%20because%20the%20status%20quo%20suits%20its%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20BNP%20leaders%20such%20as%20Mr%20Rizvi%20have%20voiced%20support%20for%20the%20campaign%2C%20the%20party%20has%20not%20spelt%20out%20its%20stand%20clearly.%20%26quot%3BOur%20policymaking%20body%20discussed%20the%20issue%20when%20some%20leaders%20wanted%20clarity%20on%20the%20party's%20stand%20on%20the%20boycott%20call.%20Till%20now%2C%20our%20party%20doesn't%20have%20any%20official%20stand%20on%20it.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20true%20that%20this%20is%20a%20call%20from%20the%20people%20and%20some%20of%20our%20leaders%20are%20supporting%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sayrul%20Kabir%20Khan%2C%20a%20member%20of%20BNP's%20media%20cell%2C%20The%20Telegraph%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711971900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2F6a26hpq_sheikh-hasina-pti_650x400_04_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-awami-league-burn-wives-sarees-sheikh-hasina-slams-rivals-for-india-boycott-call-5352149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20leaders%20demanding%20a%20boycott%20of%20Indian%20products%20must%20declare%20how%20many%20Indian%20sarees%20their%20wives%20have%20and%20why%20they%20are%20not%20setting%20these%20on%20fire%2C%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-awami-league-burn-wives-sarees-sheikh-hasina-slams-rivals-for-india-boycott-call-5352149%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-awami-league-burn-wives-sarees-sheikh-hasina-slams-rivals-for-india-boycott-call-5352149%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-awami-league-burn-wives-sarees-sheikh-hasina-slams-rivals-for-india-boycott-call-5352149%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Above-normal%20maximum%20temperatures%20likely%20during%20April-June%2C%20says%20IMD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711971886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F13%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1697178838-2097.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fabove-normal-maximum-temperatures-likely-during-april-june-says-imd-124040100683_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20Director%20General%20Mrutyunjay%20Mo