e%20it%20when%20the%20ball%20swings%20and%20the%20batters%20get%20beaten.%20Have%20tried%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20I%20can%20keep%20myself%20fit.%20The%20red-ball%20game%20teaches%20you%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20the%20ball%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20hand.%20The%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20play%20for%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaleel%20featured%20in%20six%20Ranji%20Trophy%202024%20matches%2C%20taking%2014%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2025.78%2C%20with%20the%20best%20bowling%20figures%20of%204%2F19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%20David%20Warner%20(52%20in%2035%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20a%20returning%20Prithvi%20Shaw%20(43%20in%2027%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20two%20sixes)%20started%20off%20well%20with%20a%2093-run%20opening%20partnership.%20Following%20their%20dismissal%2C%20DC%20lost%20their%20direction%20for%20a%20while%20until%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(51%20in%2032%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes)%20scored%20some%20quick%20runs%20to%20take%20the%20side%20to%20191%2F5%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatheesha%20Pathirana%20(3%2F31)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20CSK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-chase%20of%20192%2C%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%20(2%2F21)%20and%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20(3%2F21)%20troubled%20the%20CSK%20batters%20with%20their%20line%20and%20length%2C%20and%20at%20one%20point%2C%20CSK%20was%2075%2F3%20in%2010.2%20overs.%20Useful%20knocks%20came%20from%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20(45%20in%2030%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%2C%20Daryl%20Mitchell%20(34%20in%2026%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20MS%20Dhoni%20(37*%20in%2016%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes)%2C%20but%20DC%20secured%20a%2020-run%20win%2C%20restricting%20the%20five-time%20champions%20to%20171%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaleel%20got%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20for%20his%20match-winning%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20is%20in%20the%20second%20spot%20with%20two%20wins%20and%20a%20loss%2C%20giving%20them%20four%20points.%20DC%20is%20in%20the%20seventh%20spot%2C%20with%20a%20win%20and%20two%20losses%2C%20giving%20them%20two%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711971840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhb784idg_khaleel-ahmed-bcci_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fgoal-is-to-play-for-india-fast-bowler-forgotten-by-bcci-after-troubling-csk-5349112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khaleel%20Ahmed%20was%20adjudged%20as%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20for%20his%20spell%20of%202%2F21%20in%20four%20overs%20against%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Concerns%20mount%20as%20MS%20Dhoni%20spotted%20limping.%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711971685000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108946409%2Cimgsize-52928.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fconcerns-mount-as-ms-dhoni-spotted-limping-is-the-former-csk-skipper-battling-an-injury-watch%2Farticleshow%2F108946251.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20captivated%20the%20crowd%20with%20his%20electrifying%20cameo%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20on%20Sunday.%20Nonetheless%2C%20apprehensions%20persist%20regarding%20whether%20the%20former%20CSK%20skipper%20is%20contending%20in%20the%20tournament%20with%20a%20knee%20injury%2C%20a%20query%20that%20is%20troubling%20his%20fans.%20CSK%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20their%20so