tion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Match-Fixing'%20Allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fairness%20of%20the%2018th%20general%20election%20was%20challenged%20too.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20stated%20that%20Modi%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20central%20agencies%20and%20%26quot%3Bfour%20capitalists%26quot%3B%2C%20was%20indulging%20in%20'match-fixing'%20by%20arresting%20leaders%20like%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20had%20first%20accused%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhell-reveal-in-court-where-money-is-arvind-kejriwal-wifes-big-claim-5319025%5C%22%3EDelhi%20of%20facilitating%20a%20liquor%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20Kejriwal%20is%20behind%20bars%20today%20-%20was%20easily%20papered%20over.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-after-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-india-blocs-mega-show-of-strength-today-5341955%5C%22%3Ebonhomie%20between%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20leadership%20at%20this%20rally%20perhaps%20underscores%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20latter's%20plummeting%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2025%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20the%20Congress's%20overseas%20chief%2C%20held%20a%20virtual%20press%20conference%20to%20question%20the%20fairness%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-of-india-refutes-congress-allegations-on-evms-4808191%5C%22%3EElectronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20the%20presser%2C%20however%2C%20he%20skirted%20a%20question%20on%20the%20victory%20of%20his%20party%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20polls%2C%20where%20the%20same%20EVMs%20were%20used.%20Also%2C%20following%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Germany%20and%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-us-and-germany-un-speaks-on-arvind-kejriwals-arrest-5331610%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20questioned%20India's%20fairness.%20Clearly%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20frequent%20trips%20overseas%20are%20paying%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIronies%20Abound%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20was%20the%20third%20such%20event%20held%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20On%20March%203%2C%20they%20organised%20a%20mammoth%20'Jan%20Chetna%20Rally'%20in%20Patna%2C%20and%20a%20fortnight%20later%20on%20March%2017%2C%20the%20parties%20congregated%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20mark%20the%20culmination%20of%20Rahul's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20An%20impressive%20rally%20was%20held%20in%20Kolkata%20too%20on%20March%2010%2C%20but%20it%20saw%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20suo%20motu%20announce%20names%20for%20all%2042%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20TMC%20had%20stayed%20away%20from%20Rahul's%20Mumbai%20rally%2C%20and%20no%20bloc%20partners%20were%20invited%20by%20the%20party%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20whose%20spokesman%20Derek%20O'Brien%20declared%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20on%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3BTrinamool%20was%20and%20is%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20was%20the%20venue%20of%20Anna%20Hazare's%20India%20Against%20Corruption%20(IAC)%20movement%20in%202011%2C%20which%20took%20on%20the%20then-Congress-led%20Central%20government.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20which%20was%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20IAC%2C%20saw%20the%20emergence%20of%20Kejriwal%20as%20an%20anti-corruption%20crusader.%20That%20the%20same%20venue%20on%20Sunday%20saw%20a%20rally%20to%20protest%20against%20his%20incarceration%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20is%20ironic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hundred%20kilometres%20away%20in%20Meerut%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20flanked%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20alliance%20partners%2C%20including%20newcomer%20Jayant%20Choudhury%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%2C%20launched%20his%202024%20campaign%20on%20the%20plank%20of%20fighting%20corruption%20and%20ensuring%20%3Cem%3Evikas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(development).%20The%20difference%20between%20the%20BJP's%20agenda%20and%20that%20of%20its%20opponent%20is%20stark.%20Negativity%20continues%20to%20drive%20the%20Opposition%2C%20while%20Modi%20promotes%20his%20government's%20achievements%20and%20projects%20them%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btrailer%26quot%3B%20of%20things%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMamata%20Maintains%20Distance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20rally%20was%20attended%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20due%20to%20ill%20health%20rarely%20makes%20public%20appearances%20now.%20Accompanied%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Vadra%2C%20she%20sat%20beside%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20and%20Kalpana%20Soren%2C%20wives%20of%20the%20jailed%20Delhi%20and%20Jharkhand%20chief%20ministers.%20Two%20empty%20chairs%20were%20symbolically%20placed%20on%20the%20dais%20for%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Hemant%20Soren.%20Two%20other%20chief%20ministers%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20were%20absent%20from%20the%20stage.%20No%20empty%20chairs%20were%20placed%20in%20their%20honour.%20They%20were%20represented%20by%20their%20respective%20MPs.%20Mamata%20preferred%20to%20be%20in%20Krishnanagar%20on%20Sunday%20to%20campaign%20for%20Mohua%20Moitra%2C%20her%20party's%20candidate%20who%20lost%20her%20membership%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20due%20to%20a%20cash-for-query%20case.%20Notably%2C%20this%20was%20Mamata's%20first%20public%20appearance%20in%20a%20fortnight%20after%20she%20suffered%20a%20head%20injury%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20empathised%20with%20Kejriwal%20after%20his%20arrest.%20However%2C%20neither%20she%20nor%20her%20nephew%2C%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20her%20party%20who%20had%20been%20active%20in%20bloc%20meetings%2C%20found%20it%20worth%20their%20while%20to%20be%20at%20the%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20rally.%20Derek%20O'Brien%20and%20a%20new%20MP%2C%20Sagarika%20Ghose%2C%20represented%20Trinamool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20declaring%20candidates%20for%20all%2042%20seats%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20TMC%20in%20effect%20sounded%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20the%20bloc%20in%20the%20state.%20At%20Krishnanagar%2C%20Mamata%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20given%20the%20name%20for%20the%20alliance%20(sic).%20Once%20the%20election%20is%20over%2C%20I%20shall%20look%20into%20it.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20bloc%20with%20CPI%20(M)%20(Communist%20Party%20of%20India-Marxist)%20and%20Congress%20in%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%20In%20Bangla%2C%20she%20described%20the%20alliance%20as%20a%20'%3Cem%3Eghont%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(confusion)%20and%20not%20a%20'%3Cem%3Ejote%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(alliance).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternal%20Fissures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata's%20statement%20is%20an%20honest%20one.%20Her%20candour%20was%20not%20shared%20by%20other%20parties%20present%20at%20the%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20dais.%20The%20CPI%20has%20put%20up%20a%20candidate%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20it%20refused%20to%20accommodate%20the%20Congress's%20star%20campaigner%20and%20youth%20icon%20Kanhaiya%20Kumar%20from%20Begusarai%3B%20the%20RJD%20ultimately%20acquiesced%20and%20allotted%20the%20seat%20to%20the%20CPI.%20In%20Purnea%2C%20too%2C%20the%20RJD%20showed%20the%20thumb%20to%20the%20Congress%20by%20turning%20down%20the%20candidature%20of%20Pappu%20Yadav%2C%20who%20recently%20merged%20his%20party%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20nominating%20a%20recent%20defector%20to%20the%20RJD.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Congress%20state%20unit%20is%20contemplating%20'friendly%20fights'%20in%20five%20seats%2C%20miffed%20by%20the%20outcome%20of%20alliance%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20many%20fissures%20on%20the%20ground.%20Except%20for%20Mamata%2C%20however%2C%20others%20prefer%20hypocrisy%20to%20cover%20these%20clefts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Crisis%20That%20Could've%20Been%20Avoided%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20and%20Kejriwal's%20arrests%20have%20invited%20no%20censure%20from%20courts.%20Kejriwal%20avoided%20nine%20summonses%20since%20November.%20Had%20he%20showed%20up%20ab%20initio%2C%20then%20by%20now%20he%20perhaps%20would%20have%20been%20free%20to%20lead%20his%20party%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20day%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection%20from%20arrest.%20His%20lawyers%20did%20not%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20immediately.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20seized%20the%20window%20provided%20by%20the%20court's%20refusal%20and%20moved%20in.%20Kejriwal%20had%20time%20since%20November%20to%20prepare%20his%20narrative.%20But%20the%20day%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20he%20and%20his%20party%20did%20not%20have%20a%20strategy%20ready%20for%20the%20eventuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20too%20is%20frustrated%20because%20of%20the%20income%20tax%20notices%20and%20seizure%20of%20its%20funds%20by%20tax%20authorities%2C%20who%20are%20acting%20on%20court%20orders%20in%20matters%20pending%20since%201994.%20Lethargy%20and%20incoherence%20of%20Congress%20managers%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20current%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Feeble%20Response%20To%20The%20Arrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20as%20if%20AAP%20workers%20closed%20down%20the%20markets%20or%20brought%20transport%20to%20a%20standstill%20in%20protest%20against%20Kejriwal's%20arrest.%20It%20led%20to%20little%20uproar.%20The%20few%20hundreds%20who%20demonstrated%20were%20detained%2C%20taken%20to%20distant%20places%2C%20and%20let%20off.%20Life%20went%20as%20usual%20in%20Delhi.%20In%20countries%20abroad%2C%20including%20in%20neighbouring%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20mass%20protests%20are%20organised%20to%20mark%20public%20angst.%20India's%20opposition%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20limits%20itself%20to%20posting%20on%20X%2C%20holding%20200-metre-long%20marches%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Parliament%2C%20and%20sometimes%20congregating%20at%20the%20Ramlila%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20action%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20undertaking%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20All%20talk%20of%20one-on-one%20fights%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20400%20seats%20has%20fizzled%20out.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20finalised%20almost%20the%20entire%20list%20of%20candidates.%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20internal%20bickering%20and%20bargaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711971600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F02ub771s_lrc_640x480_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-whats-hurting-india-bloc-victim-mindset-lack-of-narrative-5351687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20rally%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20presented%20no%20narratives%20to%20counter%20the%20Modi%20government's%20policies%2C%20nor%20was%20an%20alternative%20agenda%20put%20on%20the%20table.%20Instead%2C%20what%20was%20apparent%20was%20a%20'victim'%20mindset.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-whats-hurting-india-bloc-victim-mindset-lack-of-narrative-5351687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-whats-hurting-india-bloc-victim-mindset-lack-of-n