h%20new%20partners%20while%20dealing%20with%20the%20increasing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-living-with-parents-save-money-housing-crisis-cost-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20dating%20app%20Wingman%2C%2065%25%20of%20users%20aged%2018-27%20choose%20to%20video%20call%20as%20a%20first%20date%20instead%20of%20meeting%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWingman%20founder%20Tina%20Wilson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20stat%2C%20taken%20from%20a%20survey%20of%20500%20users%2C%20showed%20the%20most%20notable%20shift%20since%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Gen%20Zers%20spoke%20to%20BI%20about%20the%20shift%2C%20and%20were%20broadly%20in%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsers%20in%20that%20younger%20age%20group%20just%20absolutely%20don't%20bat%20an%20eye%20at%20it%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20it's%20efficient%2C%20it's%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20a%20quick%20chat%20and%20you%20can%20see%20if%20there's%20that%20spark.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20choose%20to%20preserve%20some%20of%20the%20fun%20of%20a%20regular%20date%20%E2%80%94%20but%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20by%20ordering%20takeout%20to%20their%20date's%20place%20for%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJaded%20by%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20is%20a%20generation%20that%20knows%20what%20it%20wants%20and%20what%20it%20doesn't.%20Wilson%20said%20virtual%20first%20dates%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20weed%20people%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20whiff%20of%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20they're%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEunice%20Cycle%2C%20a%20musician%20living%20in%20Toronto%2C%20said%20she%20feels%20people%20in%20her%20generation%20are%20%26quot%3Bjaded%20by%20the%20process%20of%20dating%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20speed%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirtual%20first%20dates%20are%20less%20expensive%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20buying%20food%20and%20drinks%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20%2430%20Ubers%20there%20and%20back.%20They're%20also%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20Gen%20Z%2C%20if%20they%20are%20on%20Tinder%2C%20Hinge%2C%20or%20Bumble%2C%20they%20also%20see%20multiple%20people%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cycle%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that's%20why%20they%20might%20prefer%20Zoom%20dates%20because%20you%20could%20go%20on%20multiple%20dates%20in%20a%20day%20without%20leaving%20your%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20women%20are%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20split%20bills%20on%20first%20dates%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20an%20extra%20disincentive%20to%20going%20on%20bad%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20can't%20afford%20rent%2C%20let%20alone%20going%20on%20a%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20virtual%20dating%20%26quot%3Bjust%20an%20overall%20better%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%2C%20the%20dating-app%20founder%2C%20said%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20shame%20among%20Gen%20Zers%20making%20this%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20you've%20got%20to%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20vulnerable%20to%20get%20into%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20have%20to%20think%20about%20yourself%20first.%20And%20it's%20absolutely%20fine%20to%20say%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20I%20can't%20be%20spending%20money%20on%20a%20date.%20I've%20got%20to%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETraditional%20dating%20is%20hard%20for%20some%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELalitaa%20Suglani%2C%20a%20relationship%20expert%20at%20eHarmony%20with%20a%20doctorate%20in%20psychology%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Gen%20Z's%20embrace%20of%20virtual%20first%20dates%20offers%20convenience%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20can%20%26quot%3Bgauge%20compatibility%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bestablish%20rapport%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20way%20that's%20not%20energetically%20draining%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirtual%20first%20dates%20can%20provide%20valuable%20insights%20into%20a%20person's%20personality%2C%20communication%20style%2C%20and%20interests%20before%20meeting%20in%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%20said%20he%20much%20prefers%20speaking%20online%20rather%20than%20in%20person%20because%20he%20sometimes%20struggles%20with%20in-person%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20autistic%20and%20have%20social%20anxiety%2C%20so%20dates%20are%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20I'm%20an%20influencer%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20being%20in%20front%20of%20a%20camera%20but%20I'm%20so%20shy%20in%20real%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20people%20he%20meets%20online%20are%20happy%20to%20do%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20less%20stressful%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlotta%20Cattelani%2C%20the%20UK%20country%20manager%20at%20the%20dating%20app%20Fruitz%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20meeting%20virtually%20makes%20dates%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20able%20to%20meet%20in%20person%20for%20whatever%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20disability%2C%20availability%2C%20or%20preference%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20still%20date%20and%20meet%20new%20people%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20virtual%20date%20is%20a%20less%20formal%20chance%20to%20see%20if%20your%20match%20is%20searching%20for%20the%20same%20things%20you%20are%2C%20Cattelani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20if%20it's%20not%20going%20well%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20invent%20tedious%20small%20talk%20whilst%20waiting%20for%20the%20bill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20have%20to%20go%20offline%20eventually%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESebastian%20Garrido%2C%20a%20Gen%20Z%20digital%20marketer%2C%20told%20BI%20he's%20seen%20virtual%20first%20dates%20come%20back%2C%20and%20believes%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20effective%20way%20to%20reduce%20the%20price%20of%20the%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20doesn't%20think%20everyone%20will%20be%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20convenient%20to%20order%20your%20date's%20favorite%20food%20to%20their%20house%2C%20he%20said%2C%20plus%20you%20can%20get%20a%20good%20deal.%20This%20might%20help%20those%20who%20feel%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20first%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20reduce%20significantly%20the%20cost%20of%20your%20food%20on%20the%20date%2C%20and%20it's%20delivered%20to%20your%20partners'%20doorstep.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20pro%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20con%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20seem%20like%20you%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20a%20proper%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20money%20you're%20willing%20to%20spend%20or%20how%20much%20you%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarrie%20Berk%2C%20a%20content%20creator%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BMy%20Real-Life%20Rom-Com%3A%20How%20to%20Build%20Confidence%20and%20Write%20Your%20Own%20Relationship%20Rules%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI%20she%20understands%20the%20trend%20but%20also%20believes%20it%20has%20its%20drawbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20everything%20has%20shifted%20online%20these%20days%2C%20so%20it's%20only%20natural%20that%20dating%20moved%20into%20the%20online%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20sometimes%20we're%20on%20our%20phones%20so%20much%20we%20forget%20the%20value%20of%20that%20face-to-face%20interaction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20warns%20that%20speaking%20virtually%20cannot%20entirely%20replace%20meeting%20someone%20in%20person%2C%20so%20FaceTime%20dates%20should%20be%20used%20sparingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20began%2C%20Berk%2C%20aged%2018%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20never%20used%20a%20dating%20app.%20She%20met%20her%20first%20boyfriend%20online%2C%20speaking%20with%20him%20on%20social%20media.%20They%20dated%20virtually%20for%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20did%20meet%20this%20person%20after%20eight%20months%2C%20he%20was%20nothing%20like%20how%20he%20was%20on%20FaceTime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20I%20had%20completely%20wasted%20my%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easier%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcatfished%26quot%3B%20on%20social%20media%2C%20she%20said%2C%20because%20virtual%20dates%20cannot%20replace%20the%20chemistry%2C%20body%20language%2C%20and%20eye%20contact%20you%20might%20experience%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20humans%2C%20after%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20that%20face-to-face%20interaction%2C%20I%20think%2C%20to%20really%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20someone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-virtual-first-dates-high-cost-of-living-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711966981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f43cda3037f8e81750b396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-virtual-first-dates-high-cost-of-living-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Young%20people%20were%20virtually%20dating%20during%20the%20pandemic%20for%20obvious%20reasons.%20But%20the%20trend%20is%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-virtual-first-dates-high-cost-of-living-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'His%20grandmother%20imposed%20Emergency'%3A%20Shah%20slams%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711966823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108942972%2Cimgsize-510438.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-right-to-talk-amit-shah-slams-rahul-gandhi-for-murder-of-democracy-remarks%2Farticleshow%2F108942990.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20on%20Monday%20slammed%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20'murder%20of%20democracy%2C'%20stating%20that%20the%20Congress%20MP%20had%20no%20'right%20to%20talk'%20due%20to%20his%20grandmother%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20putting%20'lakhs%20of%20people%20in%20jail%20during%20emergency.'%20'Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20no%20right%20to%20talk%20about%20democracy%3B%20his%20grandmother%20put%20lakhs%20of%20people%20in%20jail%20during%20Emergency%2C%20banned%20parties%2C'%20the%20home%20minister%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Jodhpur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-right-to-talk-amit-shah-slams-rahul-gandhi-for-murder-of-democracy-remarks%2Farticleshow%2F108942990.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMultiple%20FASTags%20Won't%20Work%26quot%3B%3A%20Highways%20Body%20As%20New%20Norm%20Comes%20Into%20Force%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20to%20get%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20regulation%20done%20for%20your%20FASTag%20is%20over.%20Vehicle%20owners%20who%20have%20more%20than%20one%20FASTag%20for%20their%20vehicles%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20use%20the%20older%20ones%20from%20Monday%20(April%201).%20The%20other%20FASTags%20have%20been%20deactivated%20as%20part%20of%20'One%20Vehicle%2C%20One%20FASTag'%20initiative%20by%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20make%20toll%20collection%20smoother%20and%20avoid%20multiple%20e-toll%20documents%20for%20vehicles.%20The%20earlier%20deadline%20as%20February%2029%2C%202024%2C%20but%20it%20was%20extended%20till%20March%2031%20due%20to%20crisis%20in%20Paytm%2C%20under%20which%20the%20RBI%20asked%20the%20digital%20payments%20platform%20to%20not%20on%20board%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20FASTags%20won't%20work...%20People%20who%20have%20multiple%20FASTags%20for%20one%20vehicle%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20use%20all%20of%20them%20from%20today%20(April%201)%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20NHAI%20official%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFASTag%20is%20an%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20in%20India%2C%20operated%20by%20the%20NHAI.%20It%20employs%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20technology%20for%20making%20toll%20payments%20directly%20from%20the%20prepaid%20or%20savings%20account%20linked%20to%20it%20or%20directly%20toll%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20penetration%20rate%20of%20around%2098%20per%20cent%20and%20over%20eight%20crore%20users%2C%20FASTag%20has%20revolutionised%20the%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFASTag%20is%20a%20pre-paid%20tag%20facility%20for%20vehicles%20that%20allows%20non-stop%20movement%20of%20traffic%20without%20having%20to%20wait%20at%20the%20toll%20plazas.%20The%20credit%20card-sized%20document%20is%20usually%20affixed%20on%20the%20windscreen%20of%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FASTag%20KYC%20check%20has%20been%20introduced%20to%20enhance%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20and%20provide%20seamless%20movement%20at%20toll%20plazas.%20The%20highways%20body%20said%20it%20took%20the%20initiative%20after%20it%20was%20informed%20that%20more%20than%20one%20FASTag%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20a%20particular%20vehicle%20and%20FASTags%20being%20issued%20without%20KYC%20in%20violation%20of%20RBI's%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711966440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Frvlhgp