fore%20we%20should%20not%20be%20heard.%20But%20as%20a%20free%20citizen%2C%20with%20all%20my%20fundamental%20rights%20intact%2C%20I%20had%20every%20business%20to%20interfere%20and%20raise%20this%20issue.%20I%20had%20every%20right%20to%20move%20around%20freely%20on%20any%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20territory%20and%20no%20government%20had%20any%20business%20to%20cut%20away%20any%20part%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khandelwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20court%20wasn't%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20probably%20decided%20I%20really%20had%20no%20locus%20standi%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20because%20the%20emergency%20provisions%20were%20enforced%20and%20I%20had%20no%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20so%20I%20could%20not%20plead%20on%20that%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Emergency%20was%20lifted%2C%20Mr%20Khandelwal%20said%20he%20did%20not%20pursue%20the%20matter%20very%20strongly%20because%20%26quot%3Bno%20government%20was%20interested.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAfter%201977%2C%20when%20the%20emergency%20was%20lifted%20and%20the%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%2C%20I%20told%20them.%20But%20they%20asked%20me%20not%20to%20unnecessarily%20interfere%20in%20the%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20So%20I%20kept%20quiet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdismissive-congress-attitude-s-jaishankars-top-quotes-on-katchatheevu-island-row-5349734%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20Replied%2021%20Times%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20Trashes%20DMK%20Claims%20Over%20Katchatheevu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20territory%20till%201947%20and%20there%20was%20no%20dispute%20over%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20whole%20case%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20about%20the%20magnanimity%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%