C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20reduce%20GST%20on%20hybrid%20vehicles%20to%20five%20per%20cent%20and%20to%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20flex%20engines%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Finance%20ministry%20which%20is%20considering%20the%20requisition%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20he%20firmly%20believes%20the%20country%20can%20end%20fuel%20import%20by%20promoting%20the%20use%20of%20biofuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnvironmental%20activists%20welcomed%20Mr%20Gadkari's%20vision%20for%20increasing%20green%20mobility%2C%20but%20also%20struck%20a%20word%20of%20caution%20by%20flagging%20the%20use%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20the%20production%20of%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20we%20are%20still%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20a%20fossil%20fuel-based%20energy%20system%20to%20power%20electric%20cars%2C%20and%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20changed.%20There%20is%20urgent%20need%20to%20ensure%20100%20per%20cent%20renewable%20energy%20alongside%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20tackle%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Avinash%20Chanchal%2C%20a%20campaigner%20for%20Greenpeace%20India%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20said%20he%20has%20been%20pitching%20for%20alternative%20fuels%20since%202004%20and%20is%20confident%20things%20will%20change%20in%20the%20coming%20five%20to%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20give%20you%20a%20date%20and%20year%20for%20this%20transformation%20to%20take%20place%20as%20it%20is%20very%20difficult.%20This%20is%20difficult%20but%20not%20impossible%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20firmly%20believes%20that%20given%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20electric%20vehicles%20are%20being%20introduced%2C%20the%20coming%20era%20will%20be%20of%20alternative%20and%20biofuels%20and%20this%20dream%20will%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20said%20auto%20companies%20such%20as%20Bajaj%2C%20TVS%20and%20Hero%20are%2