kiosks%20in%20about%20500%20US%20restaurants%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20step%20up%20from%20nearly%20zero%20only%20two%20quarters%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Yum!%20CFO%20Chris%20Turner%20told%20investors%20in%20February.%20KFC%20plans%20to%20have%20them%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bvast%20majority%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20non-China%20restaurants%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20Turner%20said%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKiosks%20are%20lucrative%20for%20restaurants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKiosks%20reduce%20labor%2C%20meaning%20restaurants%20can%20either%20hire%20fewer%20staff%20or%20deploy%20them%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20business%2C%20like%20in%20the%20kitchen%20or%20on%20the%20drive-thru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.bls.gov%2Ftimeseries%2FCEU7072200003%3Famp%25253bdata_tool%3DXGtable%26output_view%3Ddata%26include_graphs%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewages%20go%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20more%20impetus%20on%20restaurants%20to%20look%20for%20labor%20productivity%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharon%20Zackfia%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20William%20Blair%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20With%20kiosks%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20basically%20able%20to%20arbitrage%20the%20labor%20into%20more%20value-added%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20Shake%20Shack's%20%26quot%3Bmost%20profitable%20channel%2C%26quot%3B%20Fogertey%20told%20investors%20last%20August.%20As%20well%20as%20labor%20savings%2C%20kiosk%20orders%20%26quot%3Btend%20to%20skew%20to%20dine-in%26quot%3B%20and%20thus%20use%20less%20packaging%20than%20other%20digital%20orders%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiosks%20also%20increase%20order%20accuracy%20and%20enable%20restaurants%20to%20easily%20adjust%20menu%20items%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20prices.%20And%20when%20the%20kiosks%20aren't%20in%20use%2C%20restaurants%20can%20use%20them%20to%20promote%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wendy's%20order%20kiosk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65116faee4e6ee001901cd40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20Wendy's%20kiosks%20aren't%20in%20use%2C%20it%20uses%20them%20to%20promote%20deals.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EDiners%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20splash%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20ordering%20at%20kiosks%20tend%20to%20spend%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShake%20Shack%20CEO%20Randy%20Garutti%20told%20investors%20in%20February%20that%20people%20who%20ordered%20at%20kiosks%20rather%20than%20at%20cashiers%20spent%20on%20average%20nearly%2010%25%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiosks%20can%20push%20customers%20to%20add%20drinks%20or%20sides%2C%20switch%20to%20larger%20portions%2C%20or%20add%20costly%20customizations.%20Fogerty%20noted%20that%20Shake%20Shack%20had%20introduced%20new%20technology%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20increased%20attach%20rates%20and%20customization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wendy's%20order%20kiosk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65116fade2c0220019ef408b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223468%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20order%20kiosk%20at%20a%20Wendy's%20restaurant%20in%20London.%20It%20suggested%20adding%20bacon%20and%20avocado%20to%20a%20burger.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Barish%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Jefferies%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20kiosks%20would%20%26quot%3B100%25%20of%20the%20time%20try%20to%20upsell%20you%20to%20a%20larger%20item%20or%20ask%20you%20if%20you%20want%20to%20add%20on%20french%20fries%20or%20chips%20and%20guacamole%2C%26quot%3B%20whereas%20cashiers%20at%20a%20busy%20fast-food%20restaurant%20may%20not%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20there's%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20trying%20to%20get%20through%20the%20line%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20diners%20order%20at%20kiosks%2C%20they%20feel%20less%20rushed%2C%20meaning%20they%20%26quot%3Bbrowse%20the%20menu%20and%20customize%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharon%20Zackfia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiosks%20can%20also%20promote%20items%20based%20on%20the%20time%20of%20day%2C%20season%2C%20and%20weather%2C%20like%20iced%20drinks%20on%20hot%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20some%20kiosks%20allow%20customers%20to%20scan%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-loyalty-app-deals-cheap-free-meals-prices-2024-3%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloyalty%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20collect%20points%20from%20their%20orders%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20means%20the%20kiosks%20can%20display%20personalized%20recommendations%20based%20on%20data%20they%20pull%20through%20from%20customers'%20loyalty%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20Newcastle%20kiosk%20order%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61a9dcc45d47cc0018e927d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell's%20kiosks%20in%20the%20UK%20let%20you%20collect%20loyalty-app%20points.%3Cp%3EGrace%20Dean%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ECustomers%20are%20'more%20accepting'%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20pandemic%20may%20have%20helped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20restaurants%20were%20slow%20to%20start%20introducing%20kiosks.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20industry%20operators%20for%20a%20while%20struggled%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20kiosks%20when%20effectively%20many%20consumers%20are%20walking%20around%20with%20a%20computer%20in%20their%20pocket%20to%20be%20able%20to%20order%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20Jon%20Tower%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Citi%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20restaurant