rt%20of%20video-streaming%20situation%20that%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20a%20'home'%20for%20cancelled%20content%20creators.%26quot%3B%20What%20exactly%20this%20might%20look%20like%2C%20or%20how%20many%20people%20would%20flock%20to%20it%2C%20isn't%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruth%20Social%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F03%2F27%2Ftruth-social-stock-facebook-twitter-ipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20an%20estimated%3C%2Fa%3E%205%20million%20monthly%20website%20visits%20in%20February%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20third-party%20trackers%2C%20but%20the%20company%20isn't%20revealing%20exact%20metrics%20right%20now.%20By%20comparison%2C%20Facebook%20had%20845%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%20when%20it%20went%20public%20in%202012%2C%20and%20Twitter%20had%20215%20million%20when%20it%20IPO'd%20the%20following%20year.%20The%20long%20and%20the%20short%20of%20it%20is%20that%20TMTG%20is%20not%20a%20thriving%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20maybe%20other%20social-media%20outlets%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20widest%20possible%20base%2C%20aren't%20the%20right%20comparison.%20Truth%20Social%20and%20any%20other%20business%20Trump%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Group%20spins%20up%20is%20pretty%20much%20guaranteed%20to%20appeal%20just%20to%20Trump%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20media%20company%20isn't%20the%20first%20conservative%20outfit%20to%20go%20public%20via%20SPAC%20in%20recent%20years%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fmoney%2F23755227%2Ftarget-bud-light-pride-conservative-boycott-anti-woke-lgbt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etry%20to%20make%20money%20off%20of%20right-leaning%20consumers%20and%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20predecessors%20have%20not%20done%20so%20hot.%20Rumble%2C%20a%20Peter%20Thiel-backed%20YouTube%20for%20the%20right%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-09-19%2Fpeter-thiel-backed-rumble-heads-to-the-public-markets-via-spac-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erose%20by%20some%2040%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20first%20day%20of%20trading%20in%20September%202022%20and%20has%20been%20hanging%20well%20below%20that%20ever%20since.%20Both%20Black%20Rifle%20Coffee%2C%20a%20Starbucks%20for%20Republicans%2C%20and%20Public%20Square%2C%20the%20GOP's%20supposed%20alternative%20to%20Amazon%2C%20have%20followed%20similar%20trajectories%3A%20a%20stock%20pop%20early%20on%2C%20then%20sitting%20under%20%2410%20ever%20since.%20None%20of%20them%20have%20achieved%20sustained%20profitability%2C%20though%20Black%20Rifle%20says%20it's%20on%20the%20path%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20business%20of%20anti-woke%20is%20not%20especially%20lucrative.%20As%20much%20as%20people%20say%20they%20want%20to%20shop%20and%20invest%20their%20values%2C%20it%20often%20doesn't%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20Instead%2C%20most%20people%20opt%20for%20the%20convenient%20option%20and%20whatever%20they're%20most%20used%20to%20doing%20already.%20There's%20a%20reason%20most%20boycotts%20don't%20work%20%E2%80%94%20people%20are%20busy%20and%20tired.%20It's%20true%20on%20the%20left%20as%20well.%20Dig%20deep%20enough%2C%20and%20every%20company%20in%20the%20world%20can%20probably%20give%20you%20a%20reason%20not%20to%20want%20to%20give%20them%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMight%20Trump%20and%20Truth%20Social%20be%20different%2C%20at%20least%20on%20the%20stock%20front%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20suppose%20anything%20is%20possible.%20As%20my%20colleague%20Peter%20Kafka%20points%20out%2C%20investors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-short-interest-meme-stock-gamestop-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earen't%20shorting%20the%20stock%20en%20masse%20yet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20part%20because%20doing%20so%20is%20hard%20and%20in%20part%20because%20you%20can%20see%20DJT%20taking%20off%20with%20the%20meme-stock%20crowd.%20GameStop%20and%20AMC%20weren't%20doing%20particularly%20awesome%20from%20a%20business%20sense%20when%20they%20achieved%20meme%20status%2C%20yet%20small-time%20investors%20were%20eager%20to%20pile%20into%20them.%20For%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20country%2C%20tossing%20some%20cash%20into%20Trump's%20company%20is%20not%20only%20a%20way%20to%20stick%20it%20to%20The%20Man%20but%20also%20to%20The%20Woke%20Man.%20Trump%20has%20also%20spent%20years%20insisting%20that%20his%20literal%20name%20is%20worth%20a%20ton%20of%20money%2C%20and%20I%20guess%20we're%20about%20to%20find%20out%20just%20how%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I'd%20guess%20Trump%20has%20much%20better%20odds%20of%20winning%20the%20White%20House%20(or%20ending%20up%20with%20some%20criminal%20convictions)%20than%20he%20does%20seeing%20his%20mediocre%20social-media%20company%20take%20off.%20He%20might%20want%20to%20call%20up%20someone%20on%20TMTG's%20board%20%E2%80%94%20say%2C%20his%20son%20Don%20Jr.%20%E2%80%94%20and%20see%20about%20them%20getting%20a%20meeting%20on%20the%20books%20to%20let%20him%20start%20offloading%20shares%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-stock-price-crash-spac-djt-truth-social-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711963261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6606e4313f923f7dab02ab5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-stock-price-crash-spac-djt-truth-social-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20media%20company%2C%20which%20runs%20Truth%20Social%2C%20is%20flying%20high%20a