shay-kumar-r-madhavan-ananya-panday-starrer-titled-shankara-project-to-be-backed-by-karan-johar-report%2Farticleshow%2F108938287.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Bridge%20Collapse%3A%20Process%20Of%20Clearing%20Tangled%20Wreckage%20Begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20complex%20process%20of%20clearing%20the%20tangled%20wreckage%20of%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20that%20collapsed%20spectacularly%20this%20week%20was%20set%20to%20begin%20Saturday%20with%20removal%20of%20a%20first%20section%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20killed%20six%20people%20and%20blocked%20traffic%20through%20the%20busy%20US%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20of%20many%2C%20many%2C%20many%20steps%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Maryland%20transportation%20secretary%20Paul%20Wiedefeld%20said%20at%20a%20news%20briefing.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20milestone%20as%20we%20start%20this%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoast%20Guard%20Rear%20Admiral%20Shannon%20Gilreath%20said%20a%20huge%20floating%20crane%20--%20capable%20of%20lifting%20loads%20of%20more%20than%20100%20tons%20--%20was%20set%20to%20move%20one%20fallen%20section%20of%20the%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge.%20He%20gave%20no%20details%20on%20its%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaryland%20Governor%20Wes%20Moore%20said%20the%20piece%20in%20question%20was%20not%20one%20of%20those%20pinning%20down%20the%20massive%20container%20ship%20Dali%2C%20which%20lost%20power%20Tuesday%20and%20crashed%20into%20a%20bridge%20pillar%2C%20provoking%20the%20shockingly%20quick%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoore%20said%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Btake%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20teams%20would%20eventually%20%26quot%3Bopen%20up%20a%20temporary%20restricted%20channel%26quot%3B%20allowing%20more%20tugs%2C%20barges%20and%20other%20boats%20to%20enter%20the%20area%20to%20accelerate%20the%20clean-up%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20shipping%20traffic%20is%20at%20a%20standstill%2C%20affecting%20thousands%20of%20shippers%2C%20port%20workers%20and%20others%2C%20and%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20who%20normally%20use%20the%20bridge%20each%20day%20have%20had%20to%20find%20alternative%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemoving%20the%20twisted%20steel%20remnants%20of%20the%20bridge%20and%20freeing%20the%20Dali%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20local%20authorities%2C%20who%20say%20the%20collapse%20could%20have%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20regional%20economy%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%208%2C000%20workers%20on%20the%20docks%20have%20jobs%20that%20have%20been%20directly%20affected%20by%20this%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20began%20his%20news%20conference%20by%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20six%20road%20workers%20--%20all%20Latino%20immigrants%20--%20who%20died%20when%20the%20bridge%20tumbled%20into%20the%20deep%20waters%20of%20the%20Patapsco%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20bodies%20have%20been%20recovered%2C%20while%20the%20four%20others%20have%20been%20declared%20missing%20and%20presumed%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecovery%20efforts%20have%20been%20suspended%2C%20with%20authorities%20saying%20the%20water%20--%20cold%2C%20dark%20and%20filled%20with%20jagged%20steel%20and%20concrete%20debris%20--%20is%20for%20now%20too%20dangerous%20for%20divers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711962180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7jv7msqo_baltimore-bridge-collapse_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbaltimore-bridge-collapse-process-of-clearing-tangled-wreckage-begins-5351088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20complex%20process%20of%20clearing%20the%20tan