oiled%20bottled%20water.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20strange%20taste%20persisted%2C%20the%20expectant%20mother%20suspected%20that%20someone%20might%20have%20been%20tampering%20with%20it.%20She%20then%20decided%20to%20use%20her%20iPad%20to%20video%20her%20desk%20and%20caught%20her%20colleague%20in%20the%20act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%C2%A0a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20black%20vest%20is%20seen%20approaching%20her%20desk%2C%20opening%20a%20small%20bottle%20and%20pouring%20a%20powder-like%20substance%20into%20it%20on%20the%20desk%20before%20leaving%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20employee%20took%20the%20bizarre%20step%20because%20she%20did%20not%20want%20her%20colleague%20to%20take%20maternity%20leave%20as%20she%20could%20not%20manage%20the%20increased%20workload%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-qa%3D%5C%22Component-Component%5C%22%3EThe%20victim%20has%20now%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20police%20and%20the%20authorities%20are%20investigating.%20The%20staff%20at%20her%20organisation%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%20police%20investigation%20before%20taking%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lawyer%20told%20National%20Business%20Daily%20that%20if%20the%20woman's%20actions%20were%20driven%20by%20an%20intent%20to%20harm%2C%20it%20could%20constitute%20a%20crime%20of%20injury%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20substance%20was%20toxic%20or%20caused%20actual%20physical%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20left%20internet%20users%20shocked%20and%20outraged%20at%20the%20woman's%20vicious%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Poisoning%20someone%20just%20because%20you%20do%20not%20want%20them%20to%20take%20leave%3F%20Has%20she%20been%20watching%20too%20many%20police%20dramas%2C''%20one%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''How%20did%20such%20a%20person%20even%20get%20through%20the%20exams%20to%20work%20at%20a%20government-linked%20instit