%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sankethi%20Cuisine%20co-founder%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMrs.%20Nagaratna%20Ravindra%2C%20Co-founder%20and%20Director%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBuilding%20on%20her%20foundation%2C%20my%20parents%20then%20added%20some%20methods%20to%20this%20by%20using%20a%20weighing%20scale%20to%20get%20precise%20measurements%20of%20the%20ingredients.%20This%20method%20has%20since%20become%20standardised%20across%20all%20our%20offerings%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20consistently%20deliver%20a%20taste%20that%20resonates%20the%20warmth%20and%20affection%20of%20food%20that%20is%20cooked%20with%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20optimal%20shelf%20life%2C%20Adukale%20claims%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmeticulously%20roast%E2%80%9D%20all%20other%20products%20at%20the%20ideal%20temperature.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%20incorporate%20natural%20preservatives%2C%20such%20as%20salt%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20lemon%2C%20into%20our%20recipes.%20These%20carefully%20chosen%20ingredients%20not%20only%20