n%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20about%20how%20they%20do%20it%3F%20Here%20is%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20our%20father%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20come%20true%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Ayush%20(25)%20and%20Rishabh%20(27)%20grew%20up%20watching%20their%20father%20dream%20of%20pursuing%20polyhouse%20farming.%20The%20family%20moved%20to%20Agra%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolyhouse%20farming%2C%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20greenhouse%20farming%20or%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20involves%20growing%20crops%20within%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20Polyhouses%2C%20constructed%20from%20transparent%20materials%20like%20polyethene%20or%20polycarbonate%2C%20permit%20sunlight%20penetration%20while%20trapping%20heat%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20working%20and%20could%20not%20dedicate%20full%20attention%20to%20it.%20He%20suggested%20my%20grandfather%20take%20it%20up%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20either.%20So%2C%20he%20always%20harboured%20this%20wish%2C%20and%20when%20my%20brother%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20it%2C%20we%20knew%20where%20to%20start%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ayush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20was%20in%20London%20studying%20BBA%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudying%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20coming%20back%20home%20that%20year%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20return%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5