if%20we%20ever%20became%20business%20persons%2C%20we%20would%20enter%20the%20food%20industry.%20However%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20passion%20towards%20having%20a%20farm%20motivated%20us%20to%20try%20our%20hand%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brothers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320228%2Fpune-brothers-quit-job-to-start-organic-farming-venture-worth-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20well-received%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Indian%20households%20for%20the%20relatives%20to%20have%20strong%20opinions.%20My%20father%20was%20told%20that%20he%20has%20put%20so%20much%20money%20into%20our%20education%20and%20sent%20us%20abroad%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisheartened%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20it%20was%20his%20father%20that%20gave%20them%20the%20courage.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20us%20that%20we%20need%20not%20listen%20to%20anyone.%20If%20this%20feels%20right%2C%20then%20we%20must%20continue%20with%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20nod%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20the%20brother%20duo%20decided%20to%20use%20some%20savings%20and%20loan%20some%20amount%20to%20set%20up%20the%20polyhouse%20farm%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOrganic%2C%20natural%20and%20fresh%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20the%20duo%20had%20initiated%20the%20setup%20of%20their%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20secured%20a%2040%20percent%20government%20subsidy%2C%20prompting%20us%20to%20commence%20with%20planting%20English%20Cucumber%20in%20our%20polyhouse%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20four%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20established%20their%20initial%20cultivation%20and%20harvested%20it%20within%20five%20months.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cucumber%20marked%20just%20the%20beginning.%20We%20sought%20further%20expansion%20and%20ventured%20into%20experimenting%20with%20additional%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Ayush%20recalls%2C%20while%20he%20was%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20small%20mushroom%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20sourced%20mushrooms%20from%20farmers%2C%20packed%20them%2C%20and%20sold%20them.%20Although%20brief%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20substantial%20profit%20potential%20of%20mushrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20father's%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20polyhouse%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-2-1710404232-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20father%E2%80%99s%20wish%20to%20start%20a%20polyhouse%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20when%20Ayush%20and%20Rishabh%20decided%20to%20diversify%20into%20mushrooms%2C%20they%20anticipated%20increased%20profits.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20allocate%201%20acre%20of%20the%20farm%20for%20other%20veggies%20such%20as%20cucumber%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20potatoes%2C%20and%202%20acres%20for%20mushrooms.%20We%20initiated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343926%2Feco-friendly-thermocol-kinoko-biotech-chaitanya-dubey-iit-kanpur-startup-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20and%20our%20profits%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20previous%20mushroom%20experience%2C%20Ayush%20also%20observed%20a%20trend%20in%20his%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20region%20is%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20vegetarians%20who%20favour%20mushrooms.%20Button%20mushroom%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20has%20surged%20over%20the%20years.%20With%20new%20recipes%20circulating%20online%2C%20people%20are%20relishing%20this%20chewy%20fungus.%20I%20even%20noticed%20mushrooms%20featuring%20prominently%20in%20wedding%20celebrations%2C%20with%20various%20dishes%20showcasing%20them%20as%20the%20main%20ingredient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20they%20yield%20approximately%2040%20tonnes%20of%20mushrooms%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20all%20A-grade%20mushrooms%2C%20distinguished%20by%20their%20maturity%2C%20well-formed%20shape%2C%20and%20meticulous%20trimming.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%20%E2%80%98B%E2%80%99%20grade%20mushrooms%2C%20which%2C%20due%20to%20irregular%20shapes%2C%20are%20sold%20to%20food%20processing%20companies%20for%20canning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperating%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Gupta%20Organic%20Farms%20and%20A3R%20Mushroom%20Farms%2C%20the%20brothers%20market%20their%20products%20to%20businesses%20and%20direct%20consumers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20supply%20to%20numerous%20businesses%20in%20Agra%20and%20Delhi%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20significant%20consumer%20demand%20in%20the%20city.%20In%20total%2C%20our%20monthly%20sales%20exceed%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Our%20annual%20turnover%20stands%20at%20Rs%207.5%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyush%20underscores%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20to%20its%20customers%2C%20emphasising%20that%20no%20chemicals%20are%20used%20to%20aid%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20vegetables%20and%20mushrooms%20are%20grown%20organically%2C%20without%20the%20use%20of%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20brother%20earns%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%207.5%20crore%20every%20year.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmushroom-3-1-1710404400-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344845%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20brother%20earns%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%207.5%20crore%20every%20year.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20Ayush%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20uncommon%20for%20people%20to%20look%20down%20on%20a%20profession%20like%20farming.%20People%20would%20comment%20on%20how%20there%20are%20better%20jobs%20out%20there%2C