20The%20work%20was%20suffocating%20my%20curiosity%20and%20my%20energy.%20My%20heart%20was%20just%20not%20in%20it.%20That%20is%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20service%2C%20however%2C%20Ravi%20found%20an%20avenue%20that%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20quit%E2%80%94mentoring%20UPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20aspirants.%20Since%202020%2C%20Ravi%20has%20been%20running%20a%20Free%20Online%20Mentorship%20Programme%20(FMP)%20for%20thousands%20of%20aspirants%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20the%20Chief%20Mentor%20of%20UPSC%20at%20Testbook%2C%20an%20online%20exam%20preparation%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20upon%20his%2010%20years%20of%20bureaucratic%20experience%20and%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20clinical%20psychology%2C%20Ravi%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20UPSC%20mentorship%20has%20always%20been%20geared%20towards%20mental%20fitness%20and%20motivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20results%20of%20his%20FMP%20have%20been%20promising.%20Last%20year%2C%207%20of%20his%20students%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%20This%20year%20they%E2%80%99re%20expecting%20around%2020%20students%20to%20clear%20the%20exam.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20FMP%20has%20given%20UPSC%20aspirants%20a%20choice%2C%20which%20is%20what%20stands%20out%20the%20most%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Free%20UPSC%20CSE%20Coaching%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345402%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEx-IRS%20officer%20and%20educator%20Ravi%20Kapoor%20(on%20the%20left)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognising%20the%20gap%20in%20the%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20an%20entire%20cottage%20industry%20has%20been%20built%20on%20UPSC%20coaching.%20Walk%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337715%2Fbest-chole-bhature-eateries-in-delhi-chache-di-hatti-sita-ram-diwan-chand-civil-lines-virat-kohli-ranveer-brar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20every%20second%20building%20there%20is%20running%20a%20UPSC%20coaching%20centre.%20As%20Ravi%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20this%20to%20eliminate%20the%20requirement%20for%20%5Bpaid%5D%20coaching.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20Aspirants%20wanted%20to%20consume%20my%20content%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20them%20from%20joining%20coaching%20institutes.%20They%20desire%20a%20classroom%20environment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20FMP%20did%20was%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20guidance%20