4%20which%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20presidential%20acreages%2C%20surpassing%20the%20White%20House%20in%20size.%20%E2%80%9COur%20system%20efficiently%20manages%20its%20challenging%20waste%2C%20including%20horse%20dung!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Greeneria%20collaborated%20with%20Prayagraj%20Smart%20City%20to%20illuminate%20900%20streetlights%20using%2015%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste.%20In%20Dharamshala%20and%20Belagavi%2C%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste%20power%20450%20streetlights%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20corporations%20like%20Hewlett%20Packard%2C%20and%20Capgemini%20are%20making%20strides%20in%20waste%20management.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Hinjewadi%2C%20Pune%2C%206%2C000%20employees%20from%20Hewlett%20Packard%20generate%20one%20ton%20per%20day%20(TPD)%20of%20waste%2C%20producing%2035%20kg%20of%20gas%2C%20equivalent%20to%20expensive%20LPG.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181269%2Fifs-hero-biogas-sustainability-compost-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverting%20waste%20into%20biogas%20and%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20companies%20not%20only%20reduce%20LPG%20bills%20but%20also%20obtain%20organic%20fertiliser%20as%20an%20additional%20asset%20for%20their%20large%20campuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202081px)%20100vw%2C%202081px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222081%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721.jpg%202081w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup